      "message": "also fun to figure out. i didn\u0027t see any errors without the key, and the extension is still loaded; it just can\u0027t see chrome.autotestPrivate.\n\ni\u0027m still not sure why/where the key is needed (and maybe another key could be used). this looks like it\u0027s our standard \"test key\"; it appears in a few test extensions within the chromium repository.",
      "revId": "a5087cbef1f65990bd9f136f84e0c5b81af180a3",
